    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Use Tenacious Tape Mini Patches for fixing a rip or tear on down jackets, rain gear and outdoor gear. Apply it on a puffy coat to stop feathers from leaking or quickly fix holes in sleeping bags, ski pants and gloves made of synthetic fabrics (not cotton or natural fibers). The mini patches come in a lightweight and convenient pocket pack and includes six easy-to-use 1.5” x 2.5” patches (clear and/or black nylon). With no heat or cutting required, simply peel and stick for quick, on-the-go repairs. Throw some Tenacious Tape Mini Patches in your pocket and you’ll never have to worry about ripped or damaged gear again.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">GEAR AID Tenacious Tape Mini Patches to Repair Jackets Tents Rain Gear 1.5&quot;x2.5&quot;</h2>\n  <p>Use Tenacious Tape Mini Patches for fixing a rip or tear on down jackets, rain gear and outdoor gear. Apply it on a puffy coat to stop feathers from leaking or quickly fix holes in sleeping bags, ski pants and gloves made of synthetic fabrics (not cotton or natural fibers).</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Repair holes and tears in down jackets, coats, rain gear, tents, and other outdoor gear with these easy to use, peel and stick patches; no sewing required</li>\n    <li>Use this ultra-strong adhesive tape that permanently bonds to nylon, polyester, GORE-TEX fabric, and vinyl (not for cotton, denim or natural fabrics)</li>\n    <li>Apply the six 1.5” x 2.5” patches on puffy coats, backpacks, ski pants, or gloves; sealed with a waterproof coating for full weather protection</li>\n    <li>Choose from all black nylon, all clear, or a combination of black and clear patches; nearly invisible repairs that won’t peel off during a wash</li>\n    <li>Packaging may vary</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/gear_repair/Main &amp; SWCH-T-Tape-Minis-Clear-Comp-01.jpg\" alt=\"Use Tenacious Tape Mini Patches for fixing a rip or tear on down jackets, rain gear and outdoor gear\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 01760</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 1.5 in x 2.5 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The mini patches come in a lightweight and convenient pocket pack and includes six easy-to-use 1.5” x 2.5” patches (clear and/or black nylon). With no heat or cutting required, simply peel and stick for quick, on-the-go repairs. Throw some Tenacious Tape Mini Patches in your pocket and you’ll never have to worry about ripped or damaged gear again.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
